Product Description:
4 lamp vapor tight T8 high bay for wet locations or other harsh environments.

The 4 lamp wet location/vapor tight T8 high bay is designed to provide excellent light output for the harshest environments. The fiberglass reinforced polyester housing includes a closed cell poured polyurethane gasket that completely seals the fixture against humidity, dust and corrosion. A clear acrylic lens is standard and an optional polycarbonate version is available for maximum impact resistance. All internal components are easily accessible via a removable gear tray.
